</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D9F16554FFB9BA15B4A3F347B714FB86" box="[177,1330,1063,1096]" pageId="5" pageNumber="624" type="activity">
<paragraph id="915436DFFFB9BA15B4A3F347B714FB86" blockId="5.[177,1384,717,1334]" box="[177,1330,1063,1096]" pageId="5" pageNumber="624">
<emphasis id="A39FEACDFFB9BA15B4A3F347B3BAFB86" bold="true" box="[177,412,1063,1096]" pageId="5" pageNumber="624">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Incan Little Mastiff Bat has been observed roosting in caves.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D9F16554FFB9BA15B4A0F32FB678FBBE" box="[178,1118,1103,1136]" pageId="5" pageNumber="624" type="biology_ecology">
